1. Installed WSL and Ubuntu on Windows.
2. Installed nvm with:
   curl -o- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nvm-sh/nvm/v0.39.7/install.sh | bash
3. Restarted the terminal and loaded nvm.
4. Installed Node.js version 20.16 using:
   nvm install 20.16
   nvm use 10.8.1
5. Verified installation with:
   node -v
   npm -v
6. Installed Sass version 3.7.4 using:
   npm install sass -v 3.7.4
